    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, factory-fresh condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car performs perfectly, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience as if it just rolled off the assembly line. It comes with a complete service history and has been stored in a climate-controlled environment, making it an ideal choice for a serious collector or someone who demands the absolute best.",
